291
00:22:59,430 --> 00:23:00,060
No.

292
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:02,870
We must catch them alive this time!

293
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,050
Time is running out.

294
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:07,310
Remove their weapons

295
00:23:07,710 --> 00:23:09,110
from the four windows

296
00:23:09,130 --> 00:23:10,590
and surprise attack them.

297
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,500
Okay, we'll split into four groups.

298
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:16,790
Enter through the window in three minutes.

299
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:17,790
We want them alive.

300
00:23:17,790 --> 00:23:19,390
Take one team each, go ahead.

301
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:44,620
Pan was afraid that you'd ruin it because you're inexperienced.

302
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:46,150
So he asked me to come help you.

303
00:23:46,150 --> 00:23:47,950
Don't thank me. Thank him later.

304
00:23:49,150 --> 00:23:50,110
You go first.

305
00:23:50,710 --> 00:23:51,770
Is there a problem?

306
00:23:52,470 --> 00:23:53,400
