309
00:24:03,110 --> 00:24:04,010
Ten seconds countdown.

310
00:24:04,010 --> 00:24:04,940
Handgun loaded.

311
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:06,740
Remember, catch them alive.

312
00:24:11,150 --> 00:24:12,680
Now you're scared of death?

313
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:15,910
