316
00:24:18,630 --> 00:24:20,310
that you're scared of death.

317
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:21,990
Go! Go!

318
00:24:22,510 --> 00:24:23,140
Go!

319
00:24:24,990 --> 00:24:25,670
Go!

320
00:25:56,710 --> 00:25:58,110
Ms. Guan, we've been tricked.

321
00:25:58,110 --> 00:25:59,350
Other than our men who entered,

322
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,610
