323
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:02,270
-The number of casualties.
-You are afraid of death!

324
00:26:02,270 --> 00:26:03,310
Two dead and five injured.

325
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,110
Song Zhuowen.

326
00:26:04,110 --> 00:26:06,350
You've disgraced the Police Agency!

327
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:08,350
