331
00:26:13,470 --> 00:26:15,190
Yeah, right. Stop saying stuff like that when it's already a done deed.

332
00:26:15,190 --> 00:26:16,250
You're so capable.

333
00:26:16,990 --> 00:26:19,060
Mr. Hu, you're a smart person.

334
00:26:19,710 --> 00:26:23,170
Don't you think there's something wrong with this operation?

335
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:24,750
Why was it so coincidental

336
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,080
at the first explosion?

337
00:26:26,650 --> 00:26:28,040
And no one got hurt!

338
00:26:34,310 --> 00:26:35,150
That bike

339
00:26:35,750 --> 00:26:37,480
