340
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:40,170
But it just had to screw up in front of the Public Security station.

341
00:26:40,170 --> 00:26:43,240
Nonsense! You get to say everything?

342
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:44,910
Mr. Pan.

343
00:26:45,630 --> 00:26:47,630
Every step of induction you made is very accurate.

344
00:26:47,630 --> 00:26:49,810
