352
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:04,110
Go to the hospital and take care of the injured. That's it.

353
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:05,040
How's one month?

354
00:27:05,070 --> 00:27:05,870
Four months!

355
00:27:46,150 --> 00:27:47,110
