372
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:49,190
into making money and internal feuds.

373
00:29:56,070 --> 00:29:56,930
Section Chief.

374
00:29:57,430 --> 00:29:59,110
Remove Guan Xue.

375
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:12,230
Even changing a guard dog would required feeding and training it.

376
00:30:12,230 --> 00:30:13,510
It's a waste of time.

377
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:17,720
Our mission in Harbin

378
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:22,280
