381
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:30,550
I got it.

382
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:35,730
Come in.

383
00:30:56,670 --> 00:30:58,620
In Chinese words,

384
00:30:59,910 --> 00:31:00,790
this is

385
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:03,390
